OL,3,CYoung mum warns about ketamine as she
OL,4,Cawaits potential bladder transplant
OL,6,FA young mother who spent four years
OL,7,Faddicted to ketamine is warning others
OL,8,Fof the dangers after her own addiction
OL,9,Fleft her facing the possibility of
OL,10,Fneeding a bladder transplant.
OL,12,FAmber Currah, 27, began using the
OL,13,Fpowerful drug, known widely as a horse
OL,14,Ftranquilliser, when she was 17-years-
OL,15,Fold, unaware of the long-term risks.
OL,17,FThe mum from Morecambe, now has to
OL,18,Fspend two hours a day in the bath and
OL,19,Fwear incontinence pads just to cope.
