OL,3,CYoung mum warns about ketamine as she
OL,4,Cawaits potential bladder transplant
OL,6,F"When I first tried it, I didn't love
OL,7,Fit, and then gradually over time,
OL,8,Fafter a few years had passed, I
OL,9,Fstarted taking it a little bit more
OL,10,Fand that's when I really started to
OL,11,Flike it but I found myself taking it
OL,12,Fat home every single day instead of
OL,13,Fout at parties."
OL,15,FThe 27-year-old now lives with
OL,16,Fexcruciating pain, constant burning
OL,17,Fsensations and incontinence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
