OL,3,CYoung mum warns about ketamine as she
OL,4,Cawaits potential bladder transplant
OL,6,FDoctors have warned Amber, who is now
OL,7,Fa mother to a 6-year-old son, that she
OL,8,Fnow faces the possibility of bladder
OL,9,Freconstruction or even a bladder
OL,10,Ftransplant due to extensive scarring.
OL,12,FIt comes after a recent report from
OL,13,FKing's College London, found a 20 fold
OL,14,Fincrease in deaths as a direct result
OL,15,Fof ketamine use.
OL,17,FSenior Lecturer at Kings, Dr Caroline
OL,18,FCopeland, said "We found that there
OL,19,Fwere nearly 700 deaths which have been
OL,20,Frecorded by the database that I run
OL,21,Fsince the late 1990s.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
