OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F398A1760695911
OL,3,CYoung mum warns about ketamine as she
OL,4,Cawaits potential bladder transplant
OL,6,F"But actually, over half of those
OL,7,Fdeaths have actually happened since
OL,8,F2020. So it's a problem that's
OL,9,Faccelerated massively. "
OL,11,FThe Government is considering re-
OL,12,Fclassifying ketamine from a class B
OL,13,Fdrug to class A.
OL,15,FBut researchers warn that ketamine is
OL,16,Fincreasingly being used alongside
OL,17,Fother drugs, raising doubts over
OL,18,Fwhether single-substance drug policies
OL,19,Fcan reduce harms.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
