OL,3,CYoung mum warns about ketamine as she
OL,4,Cawaits potential bladder transplant
OL,6,FAt the Oasis recovery clinic in
OL,7,FRuncorn, staff are well aware of the
OL,8,Fthreat posed by mixed drug use.
OL,10,FCentre Manager, Kerry Dare said
OL,11,F"People have always mixed drugs.
OL,13,F"We have always supported clients for
OL,14,Fpoly-use - typically it was always
OL,15,Fheroin, alcohol, and cocaine. Now it
OL,16,Fis ketamine - it is cheap and it is
OL,17,Feasily accessible, that is the issue."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
