OL,3,CYoung mum warns about ketamine as she
OL,4,Cawaits potential bladder transplant
OL,6,FAmber says the addiction has affected
OL,7,Fher whole life, and more needs to be
OL,8,Fdone to inform young people of the
OL,9,Fdangers. Amber says she had no idea
OL,10,Fketamine could cause such serious
OL,11,Fdamage.
OL,13,F"People say, 'You chose to do that,'
OL,14,Fbut I had no clue what ketamine could
OL,15,Fdo," she said.
OL,17,F"I never heard anything about it.
OL,18,FYoung people need to know this can
OL,19,Fruin your whole life."
