OL,3,CYoung mum warns about ketamine as she
OL,4,Cawaits potential bladder transplant
OL,6,FDr Niall Campbell, an addiction
OL,7,Fspecialist at The Priory, says many
OL,8,Fusers are unaware that use can cause
OL,9,Firreversible bladder damage,
OL,10,Fparticularly among teenagers and young
OL,11,Fadults.
OL,13,FHe said: "Make no mistake, this is an
OL,14,Fepidemic. It's cheap, easily available
OL,15,Fand incredibly addictive. We're seeing
OL,16,Fmore young women coming in with
OL,17,Fbladder damage that looks like
OL,18,Fchemical burns."
